<p>Hello <%= @resource.name %>,</p>

<p>Someone has recently requested to change the password for the <%= @resource.most_recent_team.name %>. You can do this through the link below:</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

<p>If you did not request a change of password, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password will not change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
